{"tid":1575091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲 918 尖咀國歌大行動","createTime":"2019-09-16T16:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T00:07:01.000Z","uid":30006,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d4cb138ac52c1eee33a172ff61b3d37601a63d","tid":1575091,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:41:59.000Z","msg":"轉貼（有殘體）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n万能朋友圈，在香港的同胞，9月18日下午1点30分至2点3O分，举目香港万人爱国，爱港人士集合尖沙嘴 ，游行唱国歌，希望各位同胞們勇跃参加活動！手拉手齊唱愛國歌曲，中国加油！中国香港加油！<br />\n<br />\n🇨🇳活動時間: 9.18日1:30pm-2:30pm(請提前15分鐘集合)<br />\n🇨🇳集合地點: 尖沙咀太子酒店<br />\n🇨🇳活動路線: 太子酒店&mdash;天星碼頭<br />\n🇨🇳活動曲目: 中華人民共和國國歌/歌唱祖國<br />\n🇨🇳著裝要求: 請勿著黑色上衣，請勿戴口罩；如有國旗/香港區旗，請攜帶出席<br />\n<br />\n⭐注: 本活動已獲警方批准，請號召親友共同參加"},{"pid":"ab2eccb122c00bb383d0cd6171b730f0d99d6199","tid":1575091,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:42:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cb9b1136e5d8fdeea33e594e75a683bb90a5eaf","tid":1575091,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"[重開][品葱轉載] [文宣戰術] 教你如何宣傳反共，緊貼現在熱門事件。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1574973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1574973</a>"},{"pid":"2723195d956ae927dcaad0dcac9e0c9b45a06a8b","tid":1575091,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.co